      &lt;img alt="" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/TSZHj4tzG1JnmivcQqed7csWGVo=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/70233479/acastro_20200723_1777_duolingo_0001.0.jpg" /&gt;
